title: MAGNUS ROBOT FIGHTER ARCHIVES Volume 2 (2013) (digital) (Son of
description:
Magnus, Robot Fighter 4000 A.D. Archives Volume 2


Hard-to-find classic sci-fi, finally collected in paperback!

In the year 4000, only one man has the power to defeat the robots that threaten mankind with slavery! Russ Manning, famous for the Tarzan and Star Wars newspaper strips, delivers a "Tarzan of the Future." Collects issues #8-#14, with a new foreword by Steve Rude!


Writers: Russ Manning, Robert Schaefer, Eric Freiwald, Herb Castle, Don Christensen
Artists: Russ Manning, Mike Royer

Genres: Superhero, Science-Fiction, Action/Adventure
Publication Date: November 20, 2013
Full Color, 200 pages
$19.99
